body:
Mordekaiser main here. I&#039;ve been following the talks of Mordekaiser updates for a bit now, and was interested, and even excited in what they were going to do... But this.. This is so incredibly stupid that it even makes my brain hurt trying to fathom why they thought this was a good idea. If the balance team ever tried to play Mordekaiser as a support or ADC replacement, you would see that he just gets harassed out of lane, and is forced to hug the tower. What changes here are going to remedy this? Oh I can get a Dragon ghost! This change alone will make up for the rest of my nonexistent laning phase! And since we&#039;re going to be losing lane 95% of the time, we&#039;ll have more time to focus on getting the dragon ghost! lol. Mordekaiser has just been **forced** to play two roles that are 100% troll for him. Do you honestly think people are going to let you pick Morde instead of an ADC? Seriously? Mordekaiser has now become the champion equivalent of revive. Never in this game&#039;s lifetime did I think riot would make such a nonsensical balance change.

P.S. His movement speed was nerfed, Have fun being kited even more than before.(and lol at the E changes)

RIP {{champion:82}}
